*Srećna* je bila što je izabrao nju. (She was happy that he chose her.)

Njena *srećna* uspomena često joj se vraćala. (Her happy memory often came back to her.)

On je bio *srećan* u društvu svojih prijatelja. (He was happy in the company of his friends.)

Ona se osećala *srećno* kad je završila zadatak. (She felt happy when she finished the task.)

Ona je *srećna* što ga je srela. (She is happy that she met him.)